column2: SELECT customers.customerid, customers.currency, AVG(transactions_1k.price / transactions_1k.amount) FROM customers INNER JOIN transactions_1k ON customers.customerid = transactions_1k.customerid GROUP BY customers.customerid ORDER BY AVG(transactions_1k.price / transactions_1k.amount) DESC LIMIT 1;
